subproject.description:
The objective of the Kiribati Diagnostic Trade Integrated Study is:
-To provide an analysis of trade-related constraints and opportunities in the economy as well as the basis for prioritizing action on them.
- To utilize this analysis to fill in gaps in the national growth and poverty reduction strategy – the KDP 2008-11.
- To mainstream priority actions and activities for supporting trade development in the annual KDP review and work programme
subproject.title: Kiribati Diagnotic Trade Study
